== 市場營銷 ==
從開拍、選角到結束的整個過程官方都未釋出任何概念圖像和設定，也不接受和電影相關的評論；直到2015年1月28日，才發布了首支前導預告和海報<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/2015/01/27/fantastic-4-teaser-poster-released/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-28 |archive-date=2015-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130003726/http://comicbook.com/2015/01/27/fantastic-4-teaser-poster-released |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://comicbook.com/2015/01/23/fantastic-four-trailer-released/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-01-28 |archive-date=2015-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130003631/http://comicbook.com/2015/01/23/fantastic-four-trailer-released |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Newsarama|Newsarama]]網站認為，預告的風格和科幻電影相似，如2014年的《[[星際效應|星際效應]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsarama.com/23350-the-fantastic-four-trailer-our-first-reactions.html|title=The FANTASTIC FOUR Trailer: Our First Reactions|author=Newsarama Staff|publisher=Newsarama|date=2015-01-27|accessdate=2015-01-29|archive-date=2015-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150129193113/http://www.newsarama.com/23350-the-fantastic-four-trailer-our-first-reactions.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該預告在網站上刷新了二十世紀福斯的觀看記錄，超越《[[X戰警：未來昔日|X戰警：未來昔日]]》<ref name="Entertainment Weekly">{{cite web |url=http://www.ew.com/node/2106722 |title='X-Men: Apocalypse': Rose Byrne returning as Moira MacTaggert -- Exclusive |author=Franich, Darren |date=2015-01-30 |accessdate=2015-01-31 |archive-date=2018-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930211610/https://www.ew.com/node/2106722 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年4月，劇組出席了[[影院業主協會|CinemaCon]]，他們在會場的表現獲得了好評<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/fantastic-four-movie-cinemacon-1201478578/ |title=Fantastic Four Footage, Cast Impress Exhibitors at CinemaCon |author=McNary, Dave |date=2015-04-23 |accessdate=2015-04-24 |archive-date=2015-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425030440/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/fantastic-four-movie-cinemacon-1201478578/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

