=== 評價 ===
《驚奇4超人》大獲負評，主要批評電影的敘事能力、節奏以及使該團隊無利可圖的動力，但演員們的表現則獲得讚譽<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/fantastic-four-review-marvel-mcu-michael-b-jordan-kate-mara-miles-teller/|title=‘Fantastic Four’ Review: 10 Minutes of Michael B. Jordan-Kate Mara-Miles Teller Chemistry, 1 1/2 Hours of Bad Story|author=Alonso Duralde|publisher=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]]|date=2015-08-04|accessdate=2015-08-04|archive-date=2015-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150805182003/http://www.thewrap.com/fantastic-four-review-marvel-mcu-michael-b-jordan-kate-mara-miles-teller/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/fantastic-four/review/813140|title='Fantastic Four': Film Review|author=Todd McCarthy|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2015-08-04|accessdate=2015-08-04|archive-date=2015-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150806144634/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/fantastic-four/review/813140|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/review/a661751/fantastic-four-review-dark-and-gritty-does-not-suit-this-marvel-muddle.html#~pkr0I4AMnXOPLx|title=Fantastic Four review: Dark and gritty does not suit this Marvel muddle|author=Emma Dibdin|publisher=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|date=2015-08-04|accessdate=2015-08-04|archive-date=2015-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150806235525/http://www.digitalspy.com/movies/review/a661751/fantastic-four-review-dark-and-gritty-does-not-suit-this-marvel-muddle.html#~pkr0I4AMnXOPLx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上根據245條專業影評只有9%的評級，平均得分3.5／10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_four_2015/|title=Fantastic Four (2015)|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2015-08-04|archive-date=2015-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109140331/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/fantastic_four_2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分27（滿分100），代表「普遍不利的評價」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/